\c 112
\s Kuropafadzwa komunhu anoda Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Rumbidzai Jehovha! Akaropafadzwa munhu anotya Jehovha, anofarira zvikuru mirairo yake.
\v 2 Vana vake vachava nesimba pasi; rudzi rwowakarurama rucharopafadzwa.
\v 3 Fuma nezvakawanda zviri mumba make; kururama kwake kunogara nokusingaperi.
\v 4 Akarurama anobudirwa nechiedza parima; iye anenyasha, netsitsi nokururama.
\v 5 Ane mufaro munhu uyo anoita nenyasha, anopa chikwereti, acharuramisirwa mhaka yake pakutonga.
\v 6 Nokuti haangatongozununguswi; akarurama acharamba achirangarirwa nokusingaperi.
\v 7 Haangatyi mashoko ezvinhu zvakaipa; moyo wake wakasimba, uchavimba naJehovha.
\v 8 Moyo wake wakasimbiswa, haangatyi, kusvikira aona kukundwa kwavadzivisi vake.
\v 9 Akaparadzira, akapa vashaiwi; kururama kwake kunogara nokusingaperi; runyanga rwake ruchakwiridzwa nokukudzwa.
\v 10 Akaipa achazviona, ndokufa neshungu; achageda-geda meno ake, ndokunyauka; kuda kowakaipa kuchaparara.
